🧠 Solitaire Stack Rule Additions:

Replace your current .addEventListener('drop',...) block with this:

javascript
col.addEventListener('drop', (e) => {
  e.preventDefault();
  const id = e.dataTransfer.getData('text');
  const card = document.getElementById(id);

  const cardValue = card.innerText;
  if (!cardValue) return;

  const target = e.target;
  let targetCard = target.classList.contains('card') ? target : target.querySelector('.card:last-child');
  let targetValue = targetCard ? targetCard.innerText : '';

  // Get rank & color
  function getRank(char) {
    return ['A','2','3','4','5','6','7'].indexOf(char);
  }

  function getColor(cardStr) {
    return /[♥♦]/.test(cardStr) ? 'red' : 'black';
  }

  const sourceRank = getRank(cardValue[0]);
  const sourceColor = getColor(cardValue);
  const targetRank = targetValue ? getRank(targetValue[0]) : -1;
  const targetColor = getColor(targetValue);

  if (target.classList.contains('foundation')) {
    if (card.innerText.startsWith('A')) {
      target.appendChild(card);
      updateScore(10);
    }
    return;
  }

  if (!targetCard || targetValue === '') {
    // Allow only Kings to go to empty column (not implemented in rank set)
    e.target.appendChild(card);
    updateScore(5);
  } else if (sourceRank === targetRank - 1 && sourceColor !== targetColor) {
    targetCard.parentElement.appendChild(card);
    updateScore(5);
  }
});

🔄 Recap of What This Does:

  • Allows valid moves only (e.g., red 6 on black 7)

  • Blocks invalid drops

  • Adds +5 score for valid moves

  • Aces still allowed on foundations (+10)

✅ Next Optional Features:

  • Deck draw pile logic (flip new cards from deck)

  • Highlight valid drop zones

  • Add win condition

javascript
function botMove() {
  if (stockPile2.length === 0) return;

  const top = stockPile2.pop();
  const card = createCard(top.rank, top.suit, true);
  waste2.innerHTML = '';
  waste2.appendChild(card);

  // Try foundation first
  const foundations = document.querySelectorAll('.foundation');
  for (let f of foundations) {
    const topCard = f.lastElementChild;
    const topValue = topCard ? topCard.innerText : '';
    const topRank = topCard ? getRank(topValue[0]) : -1;
    const topSuit = topCard ? topValue[1] : '';
    const newRank = getRank(top.rank);
    const newSuit = top.suit;

    if (f.children.length === 0 && top.rank === 'A') {
      f.appendChild(card);
      updateScore(10);
      dropSound.play();
      checkWin();
      return;
    } else if (topSuit === newSuit && newRank === topRank + 1) {
      f.appendChild(card);
      updateScore(10);
      dropSound.play();
      checkWin();
      return;
    }
  }

  // Else drop in random tableau2 column
  const tableau2 = document.getElementById('tableau2').children;
  const randomCol = tableau2[Math.floor(Math.random() * tableau2.length)];
  randomCol.appendChild(card);
  updateScore(5);
  dropSound.play();
  checkWin();
}

// Run every 4 seconds
setInterval(botMove, 4000);
